001package ltd.icecold.orangeengine.api.event;
002
003import org.bukkit.entity.Player;
004import org.bukkit.event.Event;
005import org.bukkit.event.HandlerList;
006
007import java.util.List;
008
009/**
010 * 客户端已注册模型
011 */
012public class ClientRegisterModelPostEvent extends Event {
013    private static final HandlerList handlers = new HandlerList();
014    private Player player;
015    private List<String> modelName;
016
017    public ClientRegisterModelPostEvent(Player player, List<String> modelName) {
018        this.player = player;
019        this.modelName = modelName;
020    }
021
022    public Player getPlayer() {
023        return player;
024    }
025
026    public List<String> getModelName() {
027        return modelName;
028    }
029
030    @Override
031    public HandlerList getHandlers() {
032        return handlers;
033    }
034
035    public static HandlerList getHandlerList() {
036        return handlers;
037    }
038}
